1
00:00:07,020 --> 00:00:08,140
Thank you.

2
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:16,760
(Bed 26-29)

3
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:31,219
Have you been waiting long?

4
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:32,340
I just got here.

5
00:00:32,620 --> 00:00:35,260
Have you figured out
how to handle the shareholders' meeting?

6
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:37,700
Uncle Zhaohui has Shen Tingyuan
backing him.

7
00:00:37,900 --> 00:00:39,340
But now I have you.

8
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:40,860
Besides,

9
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:43,860
I plan to use a new
strategic investment agreement

10
00:00:43,940 --> 00:00:46,220
during the voting session.

11
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,219
Wanxin,

12
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:51,699
why do you think

13
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:54,260
they never considered you
as acting chairperson?

14
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:03,620
Because I'm adopted
by Grandfather and Dad.

15
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:09,580
Don't worry. Go ahead with your plan.

16
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:11,140
I'll take care of your grandfather.

17
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:15,620
Alright.

18
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:21,240
=Echoes of Gang City=

19
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:32,280
=Episode 3=
(Love Lifts Us Higher)

20
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:41,979
CEO Xu Zhaoming of Minghui Group
has suddenly passed away.

21
00:01:41,980 --> 00:01:44,299
(In Memory of Mr. Xu Zhaoming)
Chairman Xu Qianmo remains seriously ill,

22
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:46,059
and the stock continues to fall.

23
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:49,219
A shareholders' meeting is being held today
to elect an acting chairperson.

24
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:50,219
According to predictions,

25
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:52,579
Xu Zhaohui,
the son of Chairman Xu Qianmo,

26
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:54,980
(Minghui Group)
is the most likely successor.

27
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:42,540
Uncle Zhaohui.

28
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:45,100
What are you doing here?

29
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:47,099
Shouldn't you

30
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,100
be with your grandfather?

31
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:51,940
I can handle this.

32
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:54,100
I've asked Xi to take care of him.

33
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:55,779
I just came to see

34
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:57,820
if there's anything I can help with.

35
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:02,020
Alright.

36
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:06,900
Let's begin.

37
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:11,300
Today's agenda
is to elect an acting chairperson.

38
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,740
The candidates are

39
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:14,340
Mr. Xu Zhaohui

40
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:18,300
and

41
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:20,780
Ms. Xu Wanxin.

42
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:23,540
Wait.

43
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,300
Is this a mistake?

44
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:28,419
Wanxin is about to marry Shen Hao.

45
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:29,460
Is it appropriate for her

46
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,900
to interfere

47
00:03:32,420 --> 00:03:33,779
in the family business now?

48
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:34,940
Mr. Hui,

49
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:38,499
I don't think Wanxin should accept

50
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,899
a harsh marriage arrangement like that.

51
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:42,619
That would only push Minghui

52
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:44,900
toward being taken over.

53
00:03:45,380 --> 00:03:45,979
So it seems

54
00:03:45,980 --> 00:03:47,339
Miss Xu

55
00:03:47,340 --> 00:03:49,380
is unwilling to marry Shen Hao

56
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:50,980
for the sake of Minghui.

57
00:03:52,180 --> 00:03:53,380
Wanxin,

58
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,219
I've always thought

59
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:58,180
Shen Hao and you
would make a good match.

60
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,619
Junlin Group's support

61
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:03,900
is crucial to us right now.

62
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,339
Of course,

63
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:09,220
if you don't want to marry Shen Hao,

64
00:04:09,620 --> 00:04:10,979
I won't force you

65
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:12,380
to sacrifice your marriage

66
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:14,180
for the family.

67
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:18,500
I'll sell

68
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,900
and mortgage

69
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:23,100
all my assets

70
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:26,099
to secure Junlin's help

71
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:27,380
and get us through this crisis.

72
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:29,140
I won't let anyone

73
00:04:29,380 --> 00:04:31,500
laugh at Minghui.

74
00:04:32,580 --> 00:04:33,620
Uncle Zhaohui,

75
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,740
I never said

76
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:38,180
I would cancel the marriage alliance
with Junlin Group.

77
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:43,059
I've already married

78
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:44,300
its largest shareholder,

79
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,740
Shen Gu.

80
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,500
Xu Wanxin,

81
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:02,260
you're unbelievable!

82
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:05,379
Even if you're not marrying Shen Hao,

83
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:08,580
since when does your marriage
get to be decided by you alone?

84
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:10,419
Marrying Shen Gu?

85
00:05:10,420 --> 00:05:12,420
What can he offer us?

86
00:05:33,140 --> 00:05:34,059
Where's Miss Xu?

87
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:35,540
We need a family member to sign this.

88
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:39,739
Please give it to me.

89
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:41,540
You are?

90
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,939
(Groom: Shen Gu, Bride: Xu Wanxin)

91
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:49,140
Shen Gu.

92
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,600
(Groom: Shen Gu, Bride: Xu Wanxin)

93
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,459
My apologies

94
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:08,780
for being late.

95
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:10,780
Who is this?

96
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:13,379
That's Fang Hongsheng,

97
00:06:13,380 --> 00:06:15,580
son of Lawyer Fang
and the daughter of Chen's Bank.

98
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,300
Young Master Fang,

99
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:22,820
this is Minghui's shareholders' meeting.

100
00:06:22,980 --> 00:06:24,300
What are you doing here?

101
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:26,980
Don't call me that.

102
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:30,259
I'm Mr. Shen Gu's
legal director and CFO,

103
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,420
Fang Hongsheng.

104
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,780
I'm here today

105
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,699
on behalf of Mr. Shen Gu

106
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:37,859
to announce a partnership
with Minghui Group.

107
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,459
A partnership?

108
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,020
What kind?

109
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:43,419
The contract I hold

110
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:46,900
was signed
between Ms. Xu Wanxin and Mr. Shen Gu.

111
00:06:48,340 --> 00:06:50,860
Mr. Shen has committed

112
00:06:51,340 --> 00:06:55,019
that if Minghui's stock
falls to the point

113
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:57,139
where bank loans must be repaid,

114
00:06:57,140 --> 00:07:01,019
we'll mortgage all Junlin shares we have

115
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:04,259
to help Minghui settle its debts

116
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:07,340
and stand with Minghui Group
through it all.

117
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:11,140
May I ask,

118
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:13,660
Young Master Xu,

119
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:16,180
can Shen Tingyuan

120
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:19,500
offer the same?

121
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,280
(Cooperation
and Share Guarantee Agreement)

122
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,360
(Key Commitment Terms)

123
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:34,700
What a clever niece I have.

124
00:07:35,220 --> 00:07:37,380
You know how to work behind the scenes.

125
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:45,660
Whatever Shen Gu can give you,

126
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:49,340
I can find a way to match.

127
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:50,860
But you,

128
00:07:51,660 --> 00:07:55,460
after all these years
using the Xu family name,

129
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:57,300
do you really think

130
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:59,460
you're one of us?

131
00:08:03,140 --> 00:08:04,260
Everyone,

132
00:08:05,340 --> 00:08:06,500
Xu Wanxin

133
00:08:06,980 --> 00:08:08,900
is my elder brother's adopted daughter.

134
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:10,219
She

135
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,539
has no inheritance rights.

136
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,560
(Adoption Certificate)

137
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,380
Two years ago,

138
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:22,060
due to a major mistake you made,

139
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:24,379
the company suffered a great loss.

140
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:26,580
You were forced to leave the board.

141
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,500
My dad,

142
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:31,420
Mr. Xu Zhaoming
took over all operations.

143
00:08:33,060 --> 00:08:34,979
Grandfather had the will notarized.

144
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:36,380
It clearly states

145
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:38,579
the share distribution

146
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:41,179
for every member

147
00:08:41,180 --> 00:08:43,220
of the Xu family.

148
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:48,200
(Signed by the Testator, Xu Zhaoming)

149
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:59,020
There's more good news.

150
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:02,060
Before my dad's passing,
he secured an investment deal

151
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:04,140
with a major company.

152
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:07,260
Investment?

153
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:09,019
Why don't I know about this?

154
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:10,860
Because I'm the designated contact.

155
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,740
Due to confidentiality,

156
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:14,420
I can only say

157
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:16,180
the funds have been transferred.

158
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:18,140
Check if you don't believe me.

159
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:25,819
Hello?

160
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:27,819
I'd like to confirm

161
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:29,139
if any new capital has come in.

162
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:30,500
One moment. Let me check.

163
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:33,700
Yes, the funds have just been received.

164
00:09:45,140 --> 00:09:47,260
To stabilize Minghui's stock price,

165
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,299
I will

166
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:51,540
hold a press conference
as acting chairperson.

167
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:56,580
As the largest shareholder of Junlin Group,
Shen Gu will make a statement.

168
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:18,420
It went well.

169
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,220
Got it.

170
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:23,339
Don't worry about
the press conference tomorrow.

171
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:24,500
This time,

172
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:27,940
I'm going to drive the knife
into Shen Tingyuan.

173
00:10:28,940 --> 00:10:30,060
No.

174
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:33,490
I'm going to stab it
right into his heart.

175
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:39,180
Three days.

176
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:42,380
Shen Gu has only been back
for three days.

177
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:43,939
First, he calls a shareholder's meeting

178
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:45,739
and throws our board into chaos.

179
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:47,819
Then he gets close to Xu Wanxin
without us realizing it,

180
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:49,699
and they're married.

181
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:52,299
Now they're going to hold
a press conference together.

182
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:55,140
I'm still the chairman
of Junlin Group.

183
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:58,860
He has no right
to represent Junlin Group.

184
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:01,540
I don't care whether
he represents the company or not.

185
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:04,620
I look like a complete fool right now.

186
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,580
Eight years.

187
00:11:07,220 --> 00:11:09,739
What does that make the eight years
I spent with Xu Wanxin?

188
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:10,860
Enough already!

189
00:11:11,820 --> 00:11:13,419
If you were any good,

190
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:15,740
you would've married Xu Wanxin yourself.

191
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:29,780
She chose Shen Gu.

192
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:34,540
Then she'll have to
bear the consequences.

193
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:05,179
Are you ready?

194
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:06,300
Yes.

195
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:18,700
Make it more convincing.

196
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:30,570
♪The clouds hide the faint light
behind them♪

197
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:35,670
♪A lonely bench on the street corner♪

198
00:12:36,010 --> 00:12:40,020
♪Where all feelings come to rest♪

199
00:12:41,310 --> 00:12:45,409
♪In the night sky, the moon's trail♪

200
00:12:45,410 --> 00:12:49,399
♪Stitches up and soothes my sorrow♪

201
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:52,279
♪The courage to get close to you♪

202
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:55,910
♪Drives away my hesitation♪

203
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:58,879
♪Fate turns and brings us together♪

204
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,869
♪I search my memories with all my might♪

205
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:03,779
♪Love catches me off guard♪

206
00:13:03,780 --> 00:13:05,929
♪You, in the album♪

207
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:11,110
♪Shine through my past like starlight♪

208
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:15,349
♪You fall between light and shadow♪

209
00:13:15,350 --> 00:13:19,480
♪Melting all my fears away♪

210
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:52,210
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

211
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:59,290
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

212
00:13:59,990 --> 00:14:05,380
♪You turn and look back at me♪

213
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:11,990
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

214
00:14:12,850 --> 00:14:18,500
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

215
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:25,240
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

216
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:31,680
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

217
00:14:32,830 --> 00:14:38,660
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

218
00:14:39,030 --> 00:14:46,000
♪How many letters have
I written just for you?♪

219
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:51,820
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

220
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:58,849
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

221
00:14:58,850 --> 00:15:01,729
♪The promise we made♪

222
00:15:01,730 --> 00:15:05,419
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

223
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:11,999
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

224
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:18,410
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

225
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:25,139
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

226
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:30,230
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

227
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:33,730
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪

